Comment: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:42.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Fumiyo Edogawa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:02.60,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be1}Conan Edogawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.60,0:00:06.40,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be1}An alias I use to hide my true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:09.98,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be1}Obviously, Conan Edogawa doesn't have a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:15.67,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be1}Today, let's playback the case where Conan's supposedly inexistent mother appears!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.39,0:00:19.81,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be1}In the critical moment that decides your life...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.81,0:00:21.60,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be1}You don't wanna lie to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.60,0:00:23.81,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be1}"Conan Edogawa's mom showed up," you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.81,0:00:25.82,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be1}Who the hell is she!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.82,0:00:27.28,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be1}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.28,0:00:29.15,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be1}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.15,0:00:31.66,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be1}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.56,0:00:15.67,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(400,0)\pos(421,470)\be1}Conan Edogawa
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.64,0:02:21.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Conan-{\i1}kun{\i}! Are you listening to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.93,0:02:23.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.10,0:02:24.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't "ehh" me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:28.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's been a long time since\Nyour parents transferred overseas
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:32.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and left you here!\NDon't you miss them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.11,0:02:33.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.53,0:02:40.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Geez, some parents! They don't show up once, or even call!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.28,0:02:43.12,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}Oh, man... my lie's getting busted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.75,0:02:50.09,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}Though they really {\i1}are{\i0} overseas right now, so it's not really a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.09,0:02:53.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wasn't Dr. Agasa the one who brought him here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:54.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.75,0:03:00.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then shouldn't we at least ask him\Nhow to contact his parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:02.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Y-you can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.30,0:03:04.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:07.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why not? Is there something wrong with contacting them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:13.65,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6\fad(0,200)}Oh, man! I gotta act quick or my identity as Shin'ichi Kudō will be out of the bag!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.08,0:03:16.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's here, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.45,0:03:20.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your mum!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:21.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:25.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm so sorry, Conan-{\i1}chan{\i}!\NYou must've been lonely all by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:28.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But it's all right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.08,0:03:30.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.42,0:03:32.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.13,0:03:33.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eh?! She's not your mum?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:40.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dear me! He's just being sulky,\Nafter being left alone all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:47.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My name's Fumiyo Edogawa.\NI'm Conan Edogawa's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.48,0:03:51.58,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}N-no! Conan Edogawa's an alias I invented!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:53.86,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}"Conan" can't possibly have parents!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.86,0:03:57.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I appreciate everything!\NI'll give you my thanks another day!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.86,0:03:59.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Right! I look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.74,0:04:01.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.37,0:04:05.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bye, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i}! Send us\Na letter when you get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.21,0:04:12.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Miss! Don't forget your thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:18.17,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}Bye-bye, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.55,0:04:22.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Who are you, lady?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:26.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I told you. I'm your mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.68,0:04:28.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nope! My mum's…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.23,0:04:29.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yukiko Kudō.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:36.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes. Your mother was a beautiful\NJapanese actress who enchanted men
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.28,0:04:42.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}all over the world and won all\Nthe major awards at the young age of 19.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:45.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But she fell in love with\Nthe young novelist Yūsaku Kudō,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:49.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}married at 20, and then simply retired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:53.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She later had a son, but left him\Nbehind to travel the world
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:59.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}with Yūsaku Kudō, now an\Ninternational-renowned mystery writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:05.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Isn't that right,\NShin'ichi Kudō-{\i1}kun{\i}, their only son?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.35,0:05:12.39,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}Is she with those men in black\Nwho shrunk me with their drug?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.39,0:05:13.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hold it right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.94,0:05:20.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stay still, and I'll take you to\Na nice place... A more fun place...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.57,0:05:26.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You moron, what're you doing?! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:28.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you think you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:30.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Someone catch that kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:43.76,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6\fad(0,200)}How? How did they find out who I am?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:47.47,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(0,200)\be6}Was it because I used\Nthe name "Shin'ichi Kudō"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.46,0:05:50.22,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}during the karaoke murder case?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:55.65,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}And then they heard from somewhere\Nthat I'd survived the drug...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.65,0:05:59.82,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6\fad(0,200)}Damn it! I told the inspector\Nnot to mention my name!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.49,0:06:06.66,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6\fad(200,0)}I'm so stupid! It's all my fault!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:12.20,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}What now, Shin'ichi Kudō? Should\NI go back and tell Ran everything?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.19,0:06:17.13,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}No, they'd be in danger\Nif I go back now...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:22.22,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}Dammit! What do I do?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:25.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?! He got away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:31.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes, I was careless. But it seems\Nthe boy really {\i1}is{\i} Shin'ichi Kudō...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.11,0:06:37.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see. To think he really did shrink...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:41.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}OK. Look for him. It'll be\Na pain if he goes to the cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.41,0:06:42.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But where?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.57,0:06:47.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\a6}Don't worry. His next destination\Nwill be probably be "there"...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:47.95,CharCards,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\pos(640,525)\fad(0,400)}Dr. Agasa's House
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:51.24,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}Guess I got no choice but to talk to Dr. Agasa,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:53.95,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}since he knows the situation...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:07:00.25,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}But what's taking him so long?\NWhere is he wandering around now?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:02.20,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}He's back!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.21,0:07:03.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Doc!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:12.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sweet dreams, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.81,0:07:21.27,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6\fad(200,200)}Where am I?! Seems to be a kitchen, but...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:25.49,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6\fad(200,200)}Damn it, my head's still dizzy...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:28.45,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6\fad(200,0)}I'm on the first floor!?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.45,0:07:34.16,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}I see. I was carried into this\Nold house while I was unconscious.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.16,0:07:36.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What? You {\i1}still{\i} haven't killed him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:38.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't yell at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:40.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Those were the orders from above...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.42,0:07:46.63,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6\fad(200,0)}It's that woman. And is\Nthat a man in front of her?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:52.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The organisation wants him,\Nas an example of the drug's side-effects!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.89,0:07:56.35,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}Ah! So that's why she didn't kill me!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.35,0:07:58.27,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}Still, that man...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.27,0:07:59.94,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6\fad(0,200)}W-what?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:05.73,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}Who is that masked man?!\NOh, crap! He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:09.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is he awake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.70,0:08:13.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, he's still drugged.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.12,0:08:17.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Still, is that {\i1}really{\i} the high school\Ndetective Shin'ichi Kudō?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.71,0:08:20.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I still can't believe it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:23.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But the day Shin'ichi Kudō\Nwent missing coincides
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:27.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}with the day that boy\Nappeared at that agency,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.59,0:08:32.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and all the crimes that happened\Naround him were solved easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.47,0:08:38.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The only thing I can think of is that the organisation's drug really did shrink him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:41.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then shall I try it, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.40,0:08:42.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Try?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.61,0:08:46.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I too have some of the organisation's latest poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.97,0:08:54.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I make someone take it, we can\Nfind out if it really shrinks people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.49,0:08:57.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But who do we give it to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:09:00.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The man we're dealing with tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:04.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As soon as the deal is done,\Nwe're supposed to get rid of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:06.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's the perfect chance to test the drug.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:11.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What if we do find out it shrinks people?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.68,0:09:15.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}For now, we'll just kill the man\Nwe're dealing with, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.60,0:09:17.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...get rid of the kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.93,0:09:19.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I just told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.06,0:09:25.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fscx100\fscy100}Our orders are to take the kid back so the organisation can investigate the drug's side-effects!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:28.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We can't let people know the organisation's secrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.73,0:09:29.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.53,0:09:30.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:35.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're doing things my way.\NDon't give me another corpse to carry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:37.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Understood...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:41.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Anyway, did you tell the man\Nwhere tomorrow's deal is going down?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.63,0:09:44.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes, using the usual method.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:48.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The deal is at 1:00 pm.\NGet sleep until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.64,0:09:58.14,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}Alright. They're both fast asleep...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.14,0:10:03.44,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}Yikes! He's sleeping with the mask on!? Talk about creepy!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.44,0:10:07.65,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}Anyway, I need to get these\Nropes off and get out of here!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.65,0:10:09.86,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}A wine bottle!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.86,0:10:14.56,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}Alright! Wrap it in this mat and...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:19.27,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}Crap! Did they hear that?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:23.50,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}Looks like I'm in the clear.\NOkay! Now to use a shard...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:29.30,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}I somehow managed to get the rope off...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:32.59,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}...but how do I get\Nout of this first-floor room?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.59,0:10:36.68,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}Even with the snow,\Nit'd be too dangerous to jump out...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:39.64,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}Guess my only choice is\Nto hide in that fridge...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.81,0:10:44.60,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}What's that sound?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:48.90,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}Oh! That wine must be\Ndripping somewhere...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.16,0:10:52.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-what's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:55.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What? The kid's gone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:59.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah! He was gone when I got up!\NHe must've gone out the window!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.24,0:11:00.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Damn him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:08.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He used the snow as a cushion to\Nget down! He's not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.42,0:11:12.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What're you doing?!\NLet's go find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:15.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, wait. He's still here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:19.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.14,0:11:23.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He pretended to escape,\Nand is waiting for us to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:30.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.27,0:11:33.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:43.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, my. Your hunch was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.15,0:11:46.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, he has no place to go anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:49.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}After today's deal is over,\Nwe'll find and eliminate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.30,0:11:58.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was sure I was done...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.63,0:12:03.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank goodness I found this\Nstorage area beneath the mat then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.21,0:12:11.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All right! Guess I'll look for that drug\Nwhile I have the chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:18.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Damn, can't find it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:24.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dr. Agasa said we could\Nfind a way to make me normal again
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.32,0:12:26.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}if we could figure out the drug's composition...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.62,0:12:30.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I guess he took it all\Nfor today's deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:37.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's with this newspaper?\NIt has holes all over it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.24,0:12:41.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They must've cut out letters\Nto make a message
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.77,0:12:45.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}for the guy they're dealing with...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:50.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's right! They said they're\Ngoing to kill that guy! This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.72,0:12:55.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've got to find out where the deal is,\Nstop the murder, and get the drug!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.69,0:13:02.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Guessing the missing letters\Ngives me {\i1}i-te-ho-be-ru-ka{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.24,0:13:08.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Rearranging them gives me "Beika Hotel..."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:10.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The Beika Hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:15.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But it doesn't specify where in the hotel.\NAre any other letters missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:23.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No luck, none have been cut out...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:25.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cutter marks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.80,0:13:31.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah! It was the August page\Nabove it that was cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.19,0:13:37.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Which means the August day\Nabove September 27th is... 30!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.11,0:13:42.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"Beika Hotel 30!" That's where\Ntheir deal's taking place!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:45.28,CharCards,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\pos(640,450)}Beika Hotel
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:47.82,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}But what does "Beika Hotel 30" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:52.51,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}This hotel only has 19 floors,\Nand there's no Room #30...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:55.29,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}#{\i}19? One moment, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:14:00.75,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}That's it! It could be\Na baggage number! All right!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,0:14:02.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:02.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.49,0:14:07.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My daddy lost his number tag. It's {\i1}#{\i}30...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:10.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}#{\i}30?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:14.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's strange.\NWe only have up to {\i1}#{\i}26...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:16.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh? Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.89,0:14:19.54,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}Damn! Where is it?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.52,0:14:23.90,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}Crap! It's already past noon!\NAnd the deal is at 1:00!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:27.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh no! I forgot my wallet in the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.95,0:14:28.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.82,0:14:30.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where did we park again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.37,0:14:32.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}#42. Here's the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:34.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry! I'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.16,0:14:36.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}T-the parking lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:47.88,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}This is the car parked on #30...\NCould the deal be happening in here?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:49.89,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}But there's no one inside...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.89,0:14:51.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey! What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:54.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What're you doing to our car?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:14:57.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Daddy! He must be a thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:15:01.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, it's not like that! I just\Nthought it was a cool car!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:04.61,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}These people seem\Ncompletely unrelated...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:11.32,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}Guess it's not here, either...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:13.83,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}Whoa, a huge man!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.70,0:15:19.25,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}What's he looking at?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.92,0:15:22.25,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}The parking space number?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:29.42,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}There's a small "1" written\Nin chalk next to the "30"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:33.51,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}Ah!{\i} "301{\i}" must be\Na room number at this hotel!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.51,0:15:37.78,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}And he's probably the guy\Nthey're dealing with!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:45.42,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}The masked man!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.36,0:15:49.24,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}So this{\i1} is {\i}where\Nthey're making the deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:55.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's that woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.13,0:15:57.58,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}Oh, crap! I'm trapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:16:02.21,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}That masked man will kill me\Nfor sure if he catches me again!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:06.30,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}What do I do?! What do I do?!\NWhat do I do?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:11.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}OK, Masao. The door locks by itself,\Nso you just need to close it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.88,0:16:13.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, be good while I'm gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:15.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Have fun, Mummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.18,0:16:17.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:21.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}B-burglar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:26.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shh! I'm not a bad guy!\NI'm Space Detective Conan,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.11,0:16:29.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm here to catch evil aliens\Nfrom Planet Rampō!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.94,0:16:32.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Liar! You're just a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.70,0:16:36.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm simply borrowing this\Nchild's form to deceive my foes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:38.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then show me your normal form!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.99,0:16:40.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, that's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:41.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You {\i1}are{\i} a burglar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.41,0:16:42.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:44.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just you wait! I'm gonna\Ncall the cops on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.65,0:16:47.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stop that, Masao! Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.09,0:16:50.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}T-that's my mummy's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.01,0:16:53.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm an alien from Planet Rampō!\NI can use any voice at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.89,0:16:57.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wow! That's awesome!\NYou really are a space detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:01.81,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}Looks like I managed to fool him\Nwith this voice changer...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.81,0:17:04.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey! Is there any way I can help?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.07,0:17:07.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There sure is! For now,\NI'd like to use your phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.74,0:17:09.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and do you have any chewing gum?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:13.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah! I do! But what for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.82,0:17:17.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:20.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've brought your food and wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.41,0:17:22.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eh? We didn't order any.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.91,0:17:24.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eh? But we got a call earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.92,0:17:26.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.93,0:17:30.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's fine. I {\i1}am{\i} feeling hungry.\NHave it brought in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:31.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.42,0:17:34.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Silence! Bring it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.38,0:17:36.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All right. Bring it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.39,0:17:37.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:41.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}C'mon, pick up the pace!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.57,0:17:43.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.78,0:17:48.61,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}Gum in the lock?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.11,0:17:57.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, let's start with a toast!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.57,0:18:01.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let me first introduce\Nour other guest...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:05.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Other guest?! Don't tell me\Nthat kid's under here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:09.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What? He's not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:15.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The cart's a decoy. He's really...\Ninside this closet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.37,0:18:17.71,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}Crap!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:18.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:20.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But when did he get in there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:24.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}While we were talking\Nwith the bellboy,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:28.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}he put gum in the door to\Ndefeat the automatic lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:32.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He then snuck in while we\Nwere focused on the cart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.89,0:18:38.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did you think I'd fall\Nfor such a trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.07,0:18:41.99,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}Damn! My only choice is\Nmy Anesthetic Watch Gun...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.00,0:18:43.54,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}It won't work!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.54,0:18:48.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I had that interesting watch of yours\Ndisabled after we caught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:49.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.88,0:18:53.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You'll regret the day\Nyou underestimated me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.92,0:18:57.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...high school detective Shin'ichi Kudō!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.39,0:19:03.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A toy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.89,0:19:11.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You still can't tell? It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.44,0:19:15.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The world-famous mystery writer,\NYūsaku Kudō!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.43,0:19:20.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}D- Dad? Then don't\Ntell me that lady is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.07,0:19:22.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry, Shin-{\i1}chan{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.61,0:19:23.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mum!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:29.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But the fact you couldn't tell means\NI still have the skills as an actress!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.78,0:19:32.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Which means that big guy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:33.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.21,0:19:35.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dr. Agasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.72,0:19:40.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't be so mad!\NWe were worried too, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.33,0:19:44.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, Shin-{\i1}chan{\i}! We stopped\Nby the house and you were gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:49.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And then Dr. Agasa told you\Nabout how I shrank,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.47,0:19:51.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and then you cooked up this scheme?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.87,0:19:54.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I tested your detective skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.81,0:20:00.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And you successfully followed\Nall of our clues to make it this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.45,0:20:05.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Everything was just as I had calculated,\Nuntil you were shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.24,0:20:08.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So then you knew I was hiding\Nin that kitchen's storage area?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.92,0:20:13.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Of course! Well, you just\Nbarely passed as a detective,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.43,0:20:17.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but it's your own fault for\Nnot realizing I was dressed as
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.43,0:20:20.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}the Night Baron character\Nfrom my novels!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.01,0:20:24.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You jerk! That was no time for that!\NI thought I was about to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.40,0:20:29.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, is that so? Well, what do you say\Nwe leave this dangerous country
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.77,0:20:32.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and live together leisurely overseas?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.68,0:20:34.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:35.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's right, Shin-{\i1}chan{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:40.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We did this so you would\Nrealize the situation you're in!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.65,0:20:46.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why I helped out\Nwith their act, Shin'ichi-{\i1}kun{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.12,0:20:52.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have friends in the Interpol.\NI'll have 'em look into this organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.87,0:20:57.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They'll get the drug at some point,\Nand you can be returned to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.34,0:21:01.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So let's put an end to this\Ndangerous detective game you're-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.81,0:21:03.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:07.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is {\i1}my{\i} case! {\i1}I{\i}'ll solve it!\NYou guys stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.15,0:21:08.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shin-{\i1}chan{\i}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.68,0:21:13.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Plus, I can't afford\Nto leave Japan yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.19,0:21:16.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:19.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's all right.\NLet's humour him for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.66,0:21:21.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Honey...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.19,0:21:24.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But the instant things get dangerous,\Nwe're taking you overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.93,0:21:29.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As it seems you have other reasons\Nfor not wanting to leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.44,0:21:33.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're leaving your son with us again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.91,0:21:38.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes, he insists on staying here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.08,0:21:40.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Still, Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:44.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Here is his upbringing expense.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.59,0:21:47.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Use however much of it you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.55,0:21:50.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}10 million yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.72,0:21:54.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Of course! I'd be delighted\Nto take care of your adorable
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.36,0:21:56.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and well-behaved son!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.11,0:21:59.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, and Ran-{\i1}san{\i}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.90,0:22:00.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.57,0:22:05.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please take care of him for me.\NIt seems he likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.53,0:22:07.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh! Really, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i}?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.64,0:22:09.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.12,0:22:10.70,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be6}Why, you...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.08,0:23:37.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That sure was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.75,0:23:41.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dropping my manuscripts and\Nescaping to Japan was worth it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.42,0:23:44.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But will Shin-{\i1}chan{\i} be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.04,0:23:47.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't worry.\NHe'll admit defeat sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.26,0:23:50.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey! What do you say to a trip\Naround the world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.47,0:23:51.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, that sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.55,0:23:52.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.93,0:23:58.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's the foreign magazine editors!\NHow'd they find me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.39,0:24:00.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We got a call from your son!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.14,0:24:02.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now finish the last 308 pages!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.35,0:24:03.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Screw that! I'm first!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.65,0:24:05.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He stopped {\i1}our{\i} presses!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.52,0:24:06.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He got us good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.61,0:24:08.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why that...
